---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Work/Life | Health & Wellbeing" description="How the 4-day workweek transforms mental health, reduces burnout, and promotes gender equality." active="health">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">IMPACT REPORT</span>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-8 text-on-surface">
        The Gift of <span class="italic text-primary">Time</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
        When we reclaim hours from the commute and the boardroom, we restore the human soul. Explore how the 4-day week is reshaping modern wellbeing.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-surface-container-lowest editorial-shadow rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-container">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bedtime</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg leading-none">+45m</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Daily Sleep Gain</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
      <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary-fixed opacity-30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <img alt="Meditation and peace" class="rounded-[2.5rem] w-full h-[500px] object-cover editorial-shadow grayscale-[0.2]" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDFT88pV-bzaL95RtjN29w4ODHRKRN8Lut_wHDBGUq5mo37pwVEic1yPFv2vSEkyVPX30SRUWk66xm49rr0vy8sZC4wygwyxAFFxvDz5aYZXz0CWBktqXd6jwzTe2XnOmVOEkq3pzaBqjo5uw3tXQx7bf-YatqM_in1g8VK5lRmD3QKiWYMdUXjAFwXBJXYXKoCkW3YMqRXdsNGr6oVuqeyy_xUsnwC7lm4xbO8HlRvJrQIjgOo0avXjtnqWjmsVj7RMPeN_VfSoNQ" />
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Bento Grid: The Pillars of Rest -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      <!-- Large Rest Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-[2rem] p-10 editorial-shadow border border-outline-variant/10 group">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 h-full">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl mb-4 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Radical Recovery</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Beyond just "time off," the extra day provides a buffer for deep neurological recovery. UK pilot participants reported a 71% reduction in burnout symptoms within six months.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-2">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">Burnout Risk</span>
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl">-71%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-2">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">Stress Levels</span>
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl">-39%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline-variant/20 pb-2">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">Sleep Problems</span>
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-xl">-8%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/3 bg-secondary-container rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative">
            <img alt="Family resting" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD0KsOv4FNWRNLGEZm6THPqvQNhFaFwWc-oKgryTUrTsCnGgDVdKu3eNIugb-nSZTzH-4HkO4aoGrHoJYQj4IsOZhqu3Wj8EtMSrOaL1oxxvl7zsaJ1a27zZAGzwI0D0LugWcyU_06_X2SNMZlxVtZN1lnJk0e7aTeUwBuBiXBjfYloupzVAJFsaZO91f-IBZLnI27Fdrs8VF2ORtGoI5fMDm-wpnIJ9P3Qqy8Sckzg7tv568igQheyd_rgC5EyIKiRt8ekNgTEDuU" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Exercise Card -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-tertiary-container rounded-[2rem] p-10 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-6 text-on-tertiary-container">fitness_center</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl mb-2 text-on-tertiary-container">Active Life</h3>
          <p class="text-on-tertiary-container/80 text-sm mb-6">Participants gained an average of 23.7 extra minutes of exercise per week.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-on-tertiary-container mb-2">AVG. WEEKLY MOVEMENT</p>
          <div class="h-2 w-full bg-on-tertiary-container/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-full bg-on-tertiary-container w-[85%]"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-on-tertiary-container">+2.4 hrs</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Gender Equality Stats -->
      <div class="md:col-span-12 bg-surface-container-low rounded-[2rem] p-12 border border-outline-variant/20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl mb-6">A New Era of Gender Equality</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12">
            The four-day week is more than a wellness perk; it's a structural shift in domestic labor. When everyone has more time, the "second shift" is shared more equitably.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div class="text-left p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
              <p class="text-primary font-bold mb-2">MEN'S CONTRIBUTION</p>
              <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold mb-4">+27%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Increase in childcare hours from fathers on their new day off. Men also spent 22% more time on housework.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-left p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
              <p class="text-secondary font-bold mb-2">WOMEN'S BURNOUT</p>
              <p class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold mb-4">-32%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Women experienced greater reductions in burnout and stress than men, closing the wellbeing gap.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Ludique Callout -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="bg-secondary-container p-10 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden group">
      <div class="absolute -right-8 -bottom-8 opacity-10 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-700">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[12rem]">brush</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-8 relative z-10">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-surface-container-lowest flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-secondary">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">temp_preferences_custom</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-headline text-2xl text-on-secondary-container mb-2">The Joy Factor</h4>
          <p class="text-on-secondary-container/80 leading-relaxed">
            Life satisfaction increased by 0.5 points on a 1&ndash;10 scale. While it sounds small, researchers found it equivalent to the emotional boost of a $20,000 salary increase&mdash;without the added stress.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Burnout Crisis Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20 mb-32">
    <div class="md:w-5/12">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl mb-8 leading-tight">Burnout Crisis <br /><span class="italic">Averted</span></h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
        The WHO estimates 745,000 deaths annually from overwork-related conditions. Working 55+ hours increases stroke risk by 35%. The 4-day week is preventive medicine at scale.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-2 h-12 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-2xl">65%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Reduction in Sick Days</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-2 h-12 bg-secondary rounded-full"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-2xl">39%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Less Stress Reported</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-2 h-12 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-2xl">$4</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Return per $1 Invested in Mental Health</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-7/12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <img alt="Nature connection" class="rounded-3xl h-64 w-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDO7jky9u-GyLTSwrIuuVtC7u0Zsv1rZrFksGRtQQ9Ed1kH7N4Ki3p9CiBrZGy3btHQoWjwwy3BDAYJiJOLxf4wngmw0ICr_D_4YPLt4HcZRzhQhVeDF7OWf_6coYr-WhUp0pkWPrYXolwiHOIPrUXEYOBvRNCTIOPLNk5bLP2lYaUr5Z5dkk1LuTFNqK-x_gDbC77LgNeP8j43asxIw60oX7Wf4oUDwa7pxfr0iWZnp7nNSHFtaFKdP4RL5SD0wshLUSQcGR5Kdu4" />
      <img alt="Kids playing" class="rounded-3xl h-64 w-full object-cover mt-8" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBbDNwZg3R1r4u6TtF7NnEGbrRVprbMBN6P2FbZ_bwgWrZIz3ZegrE2fwpErD_EdDog2eac1k0zHyvkC1VwmhceMXQVbg1ySSnLRRwvutk5-ni71tsMjldaLxr4sS5cEFYEAnUQJiq_-CvdNQeaOXVwTlsVUix49fFpJOofX-KMBxmpHOcB1QR7LTDIV2aHvmWH3NC8K1QXGpBIiOKwkM9hTkUkXm3Bo_eqGJ9R2G4UBnTnp0ttT6EU91U0EWIjoyOFSd1HSUq4FZo" />
      <img alt="Healthy cooking" class="rounded-3xl h-64 w-full object-cover -mt-8" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCeFH2ujPwB84qbjz4yVLRqgYfTw9o88uawSGz5F46tPE4WlSDd2xf-JUOgMTG7LcWTqaCPrv-pDaRYSUh24Ygq-_ZR9zqvdsNFLsWRN3_-ZR-cHsEXypCdH6Eml23sTk1YlEL9EzaVSy-7DGGgLkDinjc75lopULdXwyRg1tLWcRZGX2Ka4iP6qYHeNkTwkvFnwh7ioFOXf5AAMJNQE3AlGlIO0VswA6layjTQ1hP9fNvouxteaidHUk2YaWczKz_NfyEoV65f2Fw" />
      <img alt="Morning yoga" class="rounded-3xl h-64 w-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCrrQKmlZn9-paQ7xSZVvmlvXM9TTffbXo3qTZs45mwpClICCYwEfocgDlRP51eJwokOfDiPG-i79E9jNAEowy2752j2lakxjyOVCFd76qRzmxjgDzTn_HUFnOrv9BbpNgb5wbXXGL7xwnZRqKZOlYPll0XPD96lKySCxzaEDOFbfKgMVv5SZ7ktUCTTtlge9VFpvGlg7zkOfaphFEsMBNJHH6uQO5Ha1R3Ojue0Bce1ym5U-tAa5NMVjB45lOnC6vOzvOj97UYInw" />
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
